text.tspan: Check for and fix low level
You've ruled out the speaker system.
Check hardware with lspci and lshw as well
as the outputs in alsamixer and pavucontrol
Check that speakers are powered up, turned on,
and plugged into the correct jack (usually green)
on your soundcard, the *right* sound card if there
is more than one. Use the penny test on the
speakers' input plug to make sure speakers
Enable audio for the sound card
